		<h2 itemprop="name">Radio for Chromecast</h2>
		<div itemprop="description">Nowadays, we can control almost all our media with our phone. Movies with Netflix, Music with Google Play Music and local video and audio with apps like Plex. It seems like only radio is missing.<br /><br />
			So I took matters into my own hands in order to clean up my living room media-cabinet. In order to toss everything out of the cabinet expect for my tv, I made a webapplication to send my favourite radiostations to the Chromecast. And now you can too!<br /><br />
